0:16 Camera fading into V... most beautiful opening, ever!! 
0:21 Jungkook's head leaning sideways, such a soft and sad emotion as he later looks out the window, touching the window, sun shining on his beautiful face.
0:33 Jimin's tiny hands... nooo!
0:41 Jimin signaling to Jungkook "let's meet in the livingroom". Saying "Don't stay in here too long, JK... we're stronger together!"
0:55 RM softly blowing away the dust on his beloved bike, but more symbolically blowing away our sadness for us!
1:05 Jin dropping his pizza, followed by RM giving him the look! They woke up sad, but being themselves after all!
1:16 Camera fade into V again, and he then looks into the rear view mirror... we love his face just as much as the camera does... even more!
1:23 Jin... looking back at his boys. Checking on them, love and gratitude in his eyes that despite the sadness, God has taken care of all of them. Jin, you're checking on the boys and we're checking on you! 
1:29 V's most beautiful, tiny little mole on his nose! Worthy of screen time! Yesss!
1:46 THAT HUG... there are no words!
1:52 Maknae line sitting in the middle while Hyung line surrounds them. Protecting their babies, giving them the sofa... the love.
1:54 These other hugs...
1:56 Everything Suga says, EVERYTHING!
2:12 JHope smiling for us like only he can, spreading sunshine on a very gloomy day!
2:23 I cannot, CANNOT survive V's look... his eyes looking toward the stadium, his heart beating fast as he contemplates the moments with Army... a heaviness in heart but quickly gets taken over by the joy that Army brings him!
2:31 Jin watching over his boys, making sure they fall asleep first. Because a loving and protective big brother secures them first, and then when he's alone and doesn't have to be strong, he releases his pain, lets it out and prays. Only to do it all over again the next day.
2:43 ***THIS TRANSITION IS EVERYTHING!!! The beautiful melody is the echoing sound of love between BTS and Army... crying out because of the distance but knowing nothing can keep them apart!
3:02 Our boys in white surrounded by a sea of white Army lights. White representing the beauty of purity and innocence... a love so real, so true, so everlasting!

Thank you, BTS... for showing us a full day of your life in this crazy 2020. Waking up with Army on your mind, going for a healing drive round town with the boys, playing games in the living room, watching TV, eating pizza, reminiscing, falling asleep and then ending the night dreaming of a date with Army:
BTS on stage, Army surrounding them... We'll be there again, soon!
